= Ajax on Rails Intranet

by Scott Raymond for the book "Ajax on Rails", published by O'Reilly Media.

See here for information on O'Reilly's policy for code reuse:
http://www.oreilly.com/pub/a/oreilly/ask_tim/2001/codepolicy.html

